snippet.title: Music Inc.
snippet.description:
Music Inc. is a brand new music app that will allow gamers to guide aspiring musicians through the highs and lows of a music career in the 21st century. Taking control of everything from song writing and styling to recording and securing radio play, gamers will see the impact that every managerial decision has on their wannabe's career aspirations.

Available free to download from 5th February 2014.
